      • select

        public FTPResource select(URI uri,
                 Credential credential)
        Description copied from class: Module
        Return a handle on the resource identified by a URI using the given authentication factor. Subclasses should implement this to handle the module-specific details of interpretting the URI and instantiating a Resource (and its underlying Session) to access the resource indentified by the URI.
        Specified by:
        select in class Module<FTPSession,FTPResource>
        Parameters:
        uri - the URI to select.
        credential - an authentication factor, or null.
        Returns:
        A handle on the resource identified by a URI.
        See Also:
        Resource, Session
